title: The Master's Quest: The Seventh Cycle: Meet Annabella
description: Meet Annabella. She's a fast-talking, larger than life superheroine who loves nothing more than relaxing with her friends, and watching humanity thrive. When she accidentally reveals her powers to an unsuspecting stranger, her secret is out. Can she get back to the sidelines or will the world find out who she is?
author: Michael Randle Jr.
